WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
الحمد بالله رب العالمين

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.000
الرحمن الرحيم

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
مالك يوم الدين

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
إياك نعبد وإياك نستعيم

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:17.000
اهدن الصراة المستقيم

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.000
صراة الذين أنعنت عليهم

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.000
غير المغضوب عليهم

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:35.200
السلام عليكم ورحمة الله وبركاته

00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:37.200
بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:39.200
الحمد لله رب العالمين

00:00:39.200 --> 00:00:41.200
وبه نستعين ونصلي ونسلم

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:43.200
على أفضل الخلق أجمعين

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.200
نبينا محمد وعلى آله وصحبه

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:47.200
والتابعين ومن تبعهم

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:49.200
بإحسان إلى يوم الدين وبعد

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:51.200
We commence by praising Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:53.200
sending blessings and salutations

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:55.200
upon Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:57.200
and we ask Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:00:57.200 --> 00:00:59.200
to bless him and his entire household

00:00:59.200 --> 00:01:01.200
all his companions, may Allah bless them

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:03.200
and may he bless all those

00:01:03.200 --> 00:01:05.200
who have struggled and strived from the very beginning

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:08.200
to learn the deen, to put it into practice

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:10.200
to fulfill it, to convey it to others

00:01:10.200 --> 00:01:12.200
in a way that today it has got to us

00:01:12.200 --> 00:01:14.200
and we ask Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:16.200
to bless every single one of us

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:18.200
and use us also for the same

00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:20.200
and to convey the message inshallah

00:01:20.200 --> 00:01:22.200
to our offspring and to those around us

00:01:22.200 --> 00:01:24.200
in a way that we would be of service

00:01:24.200 --> 00:01:26.200
to the deen and of the inshallah

00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:28.200
earning the pleasure of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:30.200
Ameen

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:32.200
Beloved brothers and sisters, as we had said

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:35.200
in the sixth year of Hijra

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:37.200
the Prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.200
saw a dream, in his dream

00:01:39.200 --> 00:01:41.200
he saw that he was entering

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:43.200
Makkat al-Mukarrama and the Haram area

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:45.200
with his companions

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.200
and they were safe and secure

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:49.200
and some of them had shaved heads

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:51.200
and some of them their hair was very short

00:01:51.200 --> 00:01:53.200
so this was an instruction

00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:55.200
automatically from Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:58.200
because the dreams of the messengers

00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:00.200
are revelation

00:02:00.200 --> 00:02:02.200
so he got up

00:02:02.200 --> 00:02:04.200
and he told his companions

00:02:04.200 --> 00:02:06.200
I intend to fulfill Umrah

00:02:06.200 --> 00:02:08.200
it was not going to be possible

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:10.200
unless Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:02:10.200 --> 00:02:12.200
had written it

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:14.200
and so what happened is

00:02:14.200 --> 00:02:16.200
his people were quite surprised

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:18.200
but they knew that the messenger

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:20.200
صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:02:20.200 --> 00:02:22.200
if he instructed then it was to be obeyed

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:24.200
so he started off

00:02:24.200 --> 00:02:26.200
by calling the

00:02:26.200 --> 00:02:28.200
the Bedouin Arabs

00:02:28.200 --> 00:02:30.200
from the outskirts of Madina Munawwara

00:02:30.200 --> 00:02:32.200
and as he called them he said

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:34.200
let us go to Makkah

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:36.200
there is a war between us and Quraish

00:02:36.200 --> 00:02:38.200
they want to attack us, they want to harm us

00:02:38.200 --> 00:02:40.200
at the same time

00:02:40.200 --> 00:02:42.200
there is no peace between us

00:02:42.200 --> 00:02:44.200
there are so many skirmishes that took place

00:02:44.200 --> 00:02:46.200
between the battle of Khandaq

00:02:46.200 --> 00:02:48.200
the battle known as the alliance or the trench

00:02:48.200 --> 00:02:50.200
and at that particular time

00:02:50.200 --> 00:02:52.200
the following year

00:02:52.200 --> 00:02:54.200
many skirmishes took place

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:56.200
lots of different platoons

00:02:56.200 --> 00:02:58.200
were sent and much

00:02:58.200 --> 00:03:00.200
loss was suffered by the mushriks

00:03:00.200 --> 00:03:02.200
so how is this going to be

00:03:02.200 --> 00:03:04.200
possible the prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم said

00:03:04.200 --> 00:03:06.200
look the haram has been

00:03:06.200 --> 00:03:08.200
made safe, these people may decide

00:03:08.200 --> 00:03:10.200
to abuse

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:12.200
that or to

00:03:12.200 --> 00:03:14.200
disrespect the sanctity of the

00:03:14.200 --> 00:03:16.200
haram and they may even if

00:03:16.200 --> 00:03:18.200
they do decide that we are going to go

00:03:18.200 --> 00:03:20.200
without arms, without weapons

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:22.200
and we want to go in large numbers

00:03:22.200 --> 00:03:24.200
but sadly the Bedouin Arabs

00:03:24.200 --> 00:03:26.200
some of them they did not respond

00:03:26.200 --> 00:03:28.200
to Rasulullah صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:30.200
they felt in their hearts that if we

00:03:30.200 --> 00:03:32.200
were to all go to Makkah we are not going

00:03:32.200 --> 00:03:34.200
to come back and they felt in their

00:03:34.200 --> 00:03:36.200
hearts that if these people are going

00:03:36.200 --> 00:03:38.200
to go they too are not going to come back

00:03:38.200 --> 00:03:40.200
so they made an excuse to Muhammad صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:42.200
and they delayed

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:44.200
in the meantime the prophet صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:03:44.200 --> 00:03:46.200
did not delay the instruction

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:48.200
of Allah سبحانه وتعالى

00:03:48.200 --> 00:03:50.200
now let's listen very carefully because this

00:03:50.200 --> 00:03:52.200
as much as it may seem

00:03:52.200 --> 00:03:54.200
something that was not achieved

00:03:54.200 --> 00:03:56.200
by the Muslims ultimately

00:03:56.200 --> 00:03:58.200
but if you look at what happened

00:03:58.200 --> 00:04:00.200
thereafter this was the beginning

00:04:00.200 --> 00:04:02.200
of the victory of the Muslims

00:04:02.200 --> 00:04:04.200
this dream was the beginning of the

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:06.200
victory of the Muslims

00:04:06.200 --> 00:04:08.200
so the Ansar and the Muhajireen

00:04:08.200 --> 00:04:10.200
got together between one thousand

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:12.200
four hundred and one thousand five hundred

00:04:12.200 --> 00:04:14.200
men, they got together

00:04:14.200 --> 00:04:16.200
and they decided we are going

00:04:16.200 --> 00:04:18.200
with Rasulullah صلى الله عليه وسلم

00:04:18.200 --> 00:04:20.200
and they began on their path

00:04:20.200 --> 00:04:22.200
to Makkah

00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:24.200
they had taken with them

00:04:24.200 --> 00:04:26.200
the sacrificial animals

00:04:26.200 --> 00:04:28.200
at that time the Umrah was

00:04:28.200 --> 00:04:30.200
slightly different from what we have

00:04:30.200 --> 00:04:32.200
today very slightly in some

00:04:32.200 --> 00:04:34.200
of its detailed regulations

00:04:34.200 --> 00:04:36.200
and Hajj was not yet

00:04:36.200 --> 00:04:38.200
compulsory so what had happened is

00:04:38.200 --> 00:04:40.200
the people had left

00:04:40.200 --> 00:04:42.200
Al Madinah Al Munawarah

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:44.200
and they had had their Ihram

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:46.200
and at the same time they had taken their

00:04:46.200 --> 00:04:48.200
sacrificial animals and they had

00:04:48.200 --> 00:04:50.200
progressed now sacrificial animals

00:04:50.200 --> 00:04:52.200
from the pagan days

00:04:52.200 --> 00:04:54.200
they had high value in the eyes

00:04:54.200 --> 00:04:56.200
of the people if anyone saw a sacrificial

00:04:56.200 --> 00:04:58.200
animal it normally had a sign

00:04:58.200 --> 00:05:00.200
they would put a sign on it this is not

00:05:00.200 --> 00:05:02.200
to eat and so on this is for a sacrifice

00:05:02.200 --> 00:05:04.200
in the Haram people would not really steal

00:05:04.200 --> 00:05:06.200
that because it was considered

00:05:06.200 --> 00:05:08.200
highly taboo and it would bring

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:10.200
about very very bad luck

00:05:10.200 --> 00:05:12.200
on the person in fact the wrath

00:05:12.200 --> 00:05:14.200
of the Almighty so they

00:05:14.200 --> 00:05:16.200
had progressed and as they proceeded

00:05:16.200 --> 00:05:18.200
Quraish knew exactly

00:05:18.200 --> 00:05:20.200
what these people had intended

00:05:20.200 --> 00:05:22.200
they knew very well that the

00:05:22.200 --> 00:05:24.200
Muslims are coming one thousand four

00:05:24.200 --> 00:05:26.200
hundred to one thousand five hundred men

00:05:26.200 --> 00:05:28.200
and they are unarmed

00:05:28.200 --> 00:05:30.200
they only have a few swords in order

00:05:30.200 --> 00:05:32.200
to protect themselves from some perhaps

00:05:32.200 --> 00:05:34.200
attack on the road and so on

00:05:34.200 --> 00:05:36.200
but they do not intend to harm they want to

00:05:36.200 --> 00:05:38.200
come into Makkah they want to make Umrah

00:05:38.200 --> 00:05:40.200
and they want to go back to Al Madinah

00:05:40.200 --> 00:05:42.200
Al Munawarah without any violence

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:44.200
nothing besides an act of worship

00:05:44.200 --> 00:05:46.200
for the pleasure of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:05:46.200 --> 00:05:48.200
so what had happened as they

00:05:48.200 --> 00:05:50.200
had gone when they got to a place

00:05:50.200 --> 00:05:52.200
known as Usfan

00:05:52.200 --> 00:05:54.200
when they got to a place known as

00:05:54.200 --> 00:05:56.200
Usfan between Madinah and Makkah

00:05:56.200 --> 00:05:58.200
the messenger had come

00:05:58.200 --> 00:06:00.200
back to Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam whom

00:06:00.200 --> 00:06:02.200
Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam had

00:06:02.200 --> 00:06:04.200
sent to find out what was happening

00:06:04.200 --> 00:06:06.200
in Quraish what are their views

00:06:06.200 --> 00:06:08.200
so when this messenger got back

00:06:08.200 --> 00:06:10.200
he told the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa

00:06:10.200 --> 00:06:12.200
sallam Quraish has decided they are

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:14.200
not allowing you they are going to block

00:06:14.200 --> 00:06:16.200
you they are going to stop you no matter what

00:06:16.200 --> 00:06:18.200
because they feel it is against

00:06:18.200 --> 00:06:20.200
their pride and dignity

00:06:20.200 --> 00:06:22.200
to allow the enemy to come into the

00:06:22.200 --> 00:06:24.200
city even if it means to engage

00:06:24.200 --> 00:06:26.200
in an act of worship and yet Quraish

00:06:26.200 --> 00:06:28.200
in the past used to allow their

00:06:28.200 --> 00:06:30.200
enemies to come to Makkah because

00:06:30.200 --> 00:06:32.200
they had certain months in which

00:06:32.200 --> 00:06:34.200
they would not fight just to

00:06:34.200 --> 00:06:36.200
allow for those who were who wanted

00:06:36.200 --> 00:06:38.200
to fulfill their Umrah and their Hajj to come

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:40.200
in obviously at that time they

00:06:40.200 --> 00:06:42.200
used to worship idols and

00:06:42.200 --> 00:06:44.200
so on the Muslims had intended

00:06:44.200 --> 00:06:46.200
not for the sake of idols but for the

00:06:46.200 --> 00:06:48.200
pleasure of Allah the instruction of Allah

00:06:48.200 --> 00:06:50.200
subhanahu wa ta'ala and so

00:06:50.200 --> 00:06:52.200
the Quraish this

00:06:52.200 --> 00:06:54.200
man says they have sent Khalid

00:06:54.200 --> 00:06:56.200
ibn al-Waleed with an army

00:06:56.200 --> 00:06:58.200
of men approximately 100

00:06:58.200 --> 00:07:00.200
200 men there was a number of men

00:07:00.200 --> 00:07:02.200
that had left with Khalid ibn al-Waleed

00:07:02.200 --> 00:07:04.200
some narrations make mention

00:07:04.200 --> 00:07:06.200
of 200 men they were heavily armed

00:07:06.200 --> 00:07:08.200
and they were coming to charge at the

00:07:08.200 --> 00:07:10.200
Muslims now this is something very bad

00:07:10.200 --> 00:07:12.200
because the Muslims did not intend any

00:07:12.200 --> 00:07:14.200
harm they wanted to go

00:07:14.200 --> 00:07:16.200
engage in an act of worship and return

00:07:16.200 --> 00:07:18.200
so when the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:07:18.200 --> 00:07:20.200
heard that Khalid ibn al-Waleed

00:07:20.200 --> 00:07:22.200
has left with

00:07:22.200 --> 00:07:24.200
at that time he was amongst the Mushrik

00:07:24.200 --> 00:07:26.200
he had left with this little group of

00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:28.200
people in order to attack the Prophet

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:30.200
sallallahu alaihi wasallam changed his path

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:32.200
and he decided to arrive in

00:07:32.200 --> 00:07:34.200
Makkah from not

00:07:34.200 --> 00:07:36.200
from the normal path but

00:07:36.200 --> 00:07:38.200
via a place known as Hudaibiyah

00:07:38.200 --> 00:07:40.200
it was called

00:07:40.200 --> 00:07:42.200
Hudaibiyah because there was a well

00:07:42.200 --> 00:07:44.200
there known as Hudaibiyah

00:07:44.200 --> 00:07:46.200
so people might ask why is it called Hudaibiyah

00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:48.200
because of the well

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:50.200
so when the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:07:50.200 --> 00:07:52.200
got to this place known as Hudaibiyah

00:07:52.200 --> 00:07:54.200
he camped there

00:07:54.200 --> 00:07:56.200
and when he camped there

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:58.200
the Kuffar of Makkah were very uneasy

00:07:58.200 --> 00:08:00.200
because here you have

00:08:00.200 --> 00:08:02.200
Khalid ibn al-Waleed returning to Makkah

00:08:02.200 --> 00:08:04.200
telling the people of Makkah

00:08:04.200 --> 00:08:06.200
that really I did not even meet

00:08:06.200 --> 00:08:08.200
these people on the path they were too

00:08:08.200 --> 00:08:10.200
sharp and they had used a different

00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:12.200
road they had used a different route

00:08:12.200 --> 00:08:14.200
you know later on Khalid ibn al-Waleed

00:08:14.200 --> 00:08:16.200
radiallahu anhu he says whenever

00:08:16.200 --> 00:08:18.200
I fought the Muslims and whenever

00:08:18.200 --> 00:08:20.200
I engaged in anything against the Muslims

00:08:20.200 --> 00:08:22.200
I knew that Muhammad sallallahu alaihi

00:08:22.200 --> 00:08:24.200
wasallam was a protected man

00:08:24.200 --> 00:08:26.200
the man

00:08:26.200 --> 00:08:28.200
completely protected it's

00:08:28.200 --> 00:08:30.200
impossible for me to harm him or attack

00:08:30.200 --> 00:08:32.200
him this is a warrior of war

00:08:32.200 --> 00:08:34.200
telling you later on that this is the

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:36.200
messenger and his status as Allah

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:38.200
says Allah is the one who protects

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:40.200
Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:42.200
so when the path was

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:44.200
changed Khalid ibn al-Waleed came back

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:46.200
when he came back they had

00:08:46.200 --> 00:08:48.200
camped the Muslims that camped in Hudaibiyah

00:08:48.200 --> 00:08:50.200
the Kuffar of Quraysh decided

00:08:50.200 --> 00:08:52.200
to send them a man

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:54.200
officially to say do you know what

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:56.200
go and find out officially why are these people

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:58.200
here they knew but they wanted it

00:08:58.200 --> 00:09:00.200
official so they sent Budeil

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:02.200
ibn Warqa al-Khuzaa

00:09:02.200 --> 00:09:04.200
one of the leaders of Khuzaa

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:06.200
this was also the plan of Allah

00:09:06.200 --> 00:09:08.200
the plan of Allah why

00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:10.200
they sent a man who was one of the leaders

00:09:10.200 --> 00:09:12.200
of Khuzaa later on this man

00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:14.200
realized who was right and who was wrong

00:09:14.200 --> 00:09:16.200
and you will see what happened to Khuzaa

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:18.200
so this

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:20.200
Budeil ibn Warqa al-Khuzaa

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:22.200
he came to the Prophet sallallahu alaihi

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:24.200
wasallam and says I am a messenger from

00:09:24.200 --> 00:09:26.200
Quraysh in an official capacity

00:09:26.200 --> 00:09:28.200
I want to know why are you here

00:09:28.200 --> 00:09:30.200
now he is watching the Muslims

00:09:30.200 --> 00:09:32.200
he is seeing them in Ihram

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:34.200
he is seeing them with Talbiya

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.200
Talbiya means labbayk Allahumma labbayk

00:09:36.200 --> 00:09:38.200
we are at your service we have

00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:40.200
responded your call oh Allah it was a call

00:09:40.200 --> 00:09:42.200
of Allah the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:44.200
was instructed in his dream and so

00:09:44.200 --> 00:09:46.200
they were responding to the call of Allah

00:09:46.200 --> 00:09:48.200
labbayk wa sa'dayk labbayk means

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:50.200
we are at your service oh Allah

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:52.200
we have responded your call oh Allah

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:54.200
Allah calls and we respond

00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:56.200
so he heard this

00:09:56.200 --> 00:09:58.200
he was touched by it and he was told

00:09:58.200 --> 00:10:00.200
we are only here

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:02.200
in order to engage in Umrah

00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:04.200
and we will go back that's it we don't want

00:10:04.200 --> 00:10:06.200
anything extra and we will not accept

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:08.200
anything less so Budeil

00:10:08.200 --> 00:10:10.200
he understood it he went to Quraysh

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:12.200
and told them these people they don't

00:10:12.200 --> 00:10:14.200
have weaponry these people are not

00:10:14.200 --> 00:10:16.200
intending harm they are calm

00:10:16.200 --> 00:10:18.200
they are relaxed they have come with their leader

00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:20.200
in large numbers one thousand odd

00:10:20.200 --> 00:10:22.200
meaning one thousand four hundred to five hundred

